<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian nih hlanpi in thit-umnak a ser, A Thiangmi inn chungkhar si
 awkah, Hmaizah le zumh awktlak in an um nakhnga, A thiang nunnak thar an
 ngeih nak lai.

[C1]
   Thanuam in lawmhpi cio hna u si, Kan hawikom dawt thitumnak puai hi,
   Atu kan lawmhpi nak hi vancung phan seh, Vawlei an nunnak a dongh hlan
   tiang.

[V2]
 Jesuh nih Khrihfabu a dawt hna caah, A ca'h a nunnak a pek bangin, Hi
 nupi thi pa zong nih daw zungzal seh, A thiangmi cawn-piaknak ngai hna
 seh.

[C2]
   Thanuam in lawmhpi cio hna u si, Kan hawikom dawt thitumnak puai hi,
   Atu kan lawmhpi nak hi vancung phan seh, Vawlei an nunnak a dongh hlan
   tiang.

[V3]
 Bawipa, an nih cu na kut ah kan in chiah, An cungah na thluachuah
 hmunhter tuah, Ngaihchiat le lunglawmhnak hrawm ti zungzal in, An
 thawnnak nangmah ca hmang hna seh.

[C3]
   Thanuam in lawmhpi cio hna u si, Kan hawikom dawt thitumnak puai hi,
   Atu kan lawmhpi nak hi vancung phan seh, Vawlei an nunnak a dongh hlan
   tiang.</lyrics>
<title>PATHIAN NIH THITUMNAK A SER CH468</title>
<hymn_number>468</hymn_number>
</song>